            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">布里奇曼图片</span></div></div></div><p>在新译本中，陀思妥耶夫斯基的巨著成为了世界末日精神危机的独特写照。<em>萨克斯评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/fiction-the-brothers-karamazov-4776b0b1?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/august-wilson-review-staging-the-blues-d28ffa2a?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">《奥古斯特·威尔逊》评论：上演布鲁斯</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
